100 award can prove that the award was not related to the granting
101 of any abatement. In addition, any county or municipality
102 whose taxes are subject to abatement as provided in this
103 chapter, by resolution adopted by affirmative vote of a
104 majority of its members, may elect to waive the requirements
105 of this subsection.
